  "invariants": [
    "Every sentrux-core module is pub — Pro crate consumes types directly",
    "sentrux_bin::run() -> eframe::Result<()> signature is load-bearing for Pro wrapper",
    "license::init() runs BEFORE any GUI/CLI work in run()",
    "sync_embedded_plugins() runs AFTER ensure_grammars_installed() — embedded overrides tarball",
    "Free-tier code never assumes pro.dylib is present — degrade silently via pro_registry",
    "Never gate features with tier.is_pro() — use pro_registry lookup instead",
    "LICENSE_PUBLIC_KEY in license.rs is paired with offline private key — changing invalidates all issued licenses"
  ],
  "do_not_touch": [
    "target/",
    "assets/*.gif",
    "assets/logo-*.svg",
    "docs/*.html",
    "LICENSE_PUBLIC_KEY constant in sentrux-core/src/license.rs"
  ],
